Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,完成使命，让航天局以你们为荣吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's make NASA proud today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(430,198)\an6}第18个太阳日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你那边情况如何，沃特尼？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: How's it looking over there, Watney?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你问了，很高兴告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: Well, you'll be happy to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在14到28区内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that in Grid Section 14-28,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,土壤微粒大部分都很粗糙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the particles were predominantly coarse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，29区的土壤质量较好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but in 29, they're much finer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,应该可以用作化学分析\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they should be ideal for chem analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦，大家听到了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: Oh, wow. Did everybody hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,马克的重大发现是一堆烂泥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mark just discovered dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这事儿我们得通知媒体吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}(LAUGHS) Should we alert the media?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天又做了什么，马丁内兹？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: Sorry, what are you doing today, Martinez?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还是让飞行器立正站好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Making sure the MAV is still upright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我得让你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: I'd like you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行设备的外观检查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that visual inspection of the equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对任务成功执行至关重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is imperative to mission success.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想让你知道，飞行器的确站的很直\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I also would like to report that the MAV is still upright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: (SIGHS) Watney,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你无线电一直开着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you keep leaving your channel open...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁内兹就会一直找你说个不停\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which leads to Martinez responding...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就都得听你俩闲扯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which leads to all of us listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去我就要发飙了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which leads to me being annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁内兹，队长希望你能闭上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Martinez, the captain would like you to please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你那“能说会道”的嘴巴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}shut your smart mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(LAUGHING)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望你能换个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'd prefer to use a different adjective
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,来形容马丁内兹的嘴巴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to describe Martinez's mouth. (WATNEY LAUGHING)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,贝克这话是在讽刺我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: Did Beck just insult me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,第一，人家是贝克医生；第二，他确实是在讽刺你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: "Dr. Beck." And yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，我很乐意把他们的无线电关掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Happy to turn the radios off from here, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你下命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，约翰森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait, Johanssen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,执行任务时，不间断的通讯是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Constant communication is the hallmark...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们关掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shut 'em off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}(BEEPS) WATNEY: No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样对我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我替家乡的小伙们向你道歉，沃格尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: I apologize for my countrymen, Vogel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VOGEL: Accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，我们需要多少样本？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How many samples do we need, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,7个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,每个100克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}100 grams each.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(ALARM BLARING)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,任务有更新，是风暴预警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have a mission update. A storm warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，你现在能回居住舱吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commander, you should come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有个东西需要你看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're gonna want to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,风暴预警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}JOHANSSEN: A storm warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我在今早的简报看过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: I saw that in this morning's briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能在风暴到达前完成任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be inside before it hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是没错，但是他们提升了预警强度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, they upgraded their estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,情况要比之前糟的多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The storm's gonna be a lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁内兹，你那边情况如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Martinez, how does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很不妙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,风暴直径1200公里，方向24.41度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"1,200 kilometers in diameter, bearing 24.41 degrees."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,直冲我们而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's tracking right towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,根据当前风暴等级\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Based on current escalation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,风力可达约8600牛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"estimated force of 8,600 newtons."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最多能承受多大风力？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the abort force?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,7500牛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}7,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只要高于这个数值，飞行器就会侧倾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: Anything more than that and the MAV could tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要取消任务吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do we scrub?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,准备撤离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Begin abort procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,预估数据会存在一定的误差\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VOGEL: We are estimating with a margin of error.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以等风暴过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We could wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等风暴过去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: Let's wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等等吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，你怎么说？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}JOHANSSEN: Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,准备紧急撤离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Prep emergency departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,队长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,任务取消了，这是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: We're scrubbed. That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁内兹，距发射还有多长时间？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Martinez, how long before take-off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,12分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}12 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(ALARM BLARING)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,能见度几乎为零\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Visibility is almost zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人失去联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anyone gets lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就通过遥测定位来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}hone in on my suit's telemetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大家准备好没？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(ALL GROAN)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，你没事吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: Commander, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(WIND HOWLING)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(STRAINING)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(BREATHING HEAVILY)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，倾斜度已经达到10度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commander, we're at 10 degrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,到12.3度就会发生侧翻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the MAV is gonna tip at 12.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！我想我有办法阻止倾斜了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: Hey! We might be able to keep the MAV from tipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么办法？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,用通讯杆的电缆把飞行器…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Use the cables from the comms mast as guy-lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,绑到探测车上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}anchor it with the Rover's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大家小心！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(WATNEY GROANS)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(SCREAMING)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特尼！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Watney!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,警报，检测到宇航服破裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}FEMALE AUTOMATED VOICE: Warning. Suit breach detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特尼被击中了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特尼，回答我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Watney, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在遥测失灵前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Before we lost telemetry,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他的失压警报也响了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}his decompression alarm went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰森，他最后的位置在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Where did you last see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他的生命体征如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: What are the vitals on his suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他掉线了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去了和他的一切联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}BECK: A complete loss of signal on Watney.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 贝克！- 怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VOGEL: Beck! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,宇航服失压，他能存活多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long can he survive decompression?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不到一分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Less than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大家排好队，往西走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Line up, walk west.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能趴在地上，我们别错过他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He may be prone. We don't wanna step over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,队长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,倾斜度已经达到10.5度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're at 10.5 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,警报，严重倾斜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}FEMALE AUTOMATED VOICE: Warning. Excessive tilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在风力作用下会继续倾斜到11度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tilting to 11 with all the gusts of wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人，定位马丁内兹的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone, hone in on Martinez's suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们回气密舱，准备发射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll get you to airlock. Get in, prep for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那你呢，队长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}BECK: What about you, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我接着找，你们行动！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna search a little longer. Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特尼！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Watney!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特尼，听到请回答！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Watney, report!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行器现在倾斜11.6度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: The MAV's at 11.6 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一阵强风就要倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One good gust and we're tipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果撑不住了，你就发射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it tips, you launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你真以为我会抛下你们吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You really think I'm gonna leave you behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令，马丁内兹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: That's an order, Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,马克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mark! (BECK GRUNTING)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,马克！能听到吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mark! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁内兹，近距雷达能派上用场吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Martinez, what about the proximity radar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:06:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,它能不能检测到沃特尼的位置？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could that detect Watney's suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,近距雷达是为了勘测赫尔墨斯号的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: It's made to see the Hermes from orbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它可测不到宇航服上的一块小金属\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not a little piece of metal from a single suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,试一试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她在干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VOGEL: What is she thinking? She knows
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她明知道红外线没法穿透风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the infrared can't get through a sandstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会放弃任何一个希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}BECK: She's grasping for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没有信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: We've got negative contact
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,近距雷达无法定位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on the proximity radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,完全无法定位？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，就连居住舱都看不清\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: No. I can barely see the Hab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，我知道你不想听这句话，但是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commander, I know you don't wanna hear this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,马克已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mark is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,队长！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,贝克，你说话不经大脑吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, what the hell is wrong with you, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友刚刚去世\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My friend just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想队长也遭遇不幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want my commander to die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,失衡警报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}FEMALE AUTOMATED VOICE: Stability warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要侧倾了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're tipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，你现在就得回来！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}BECK: Commander, you need to get back to the ship, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,13度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: 13 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果失去平衡，我们就都完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we pass balance, we'll never rock back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我还剩一个办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: I've got one more trick left,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但接下来我就只能执行命令了，队长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then I'm following orders, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然用燃料保持平衡？！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're firing the OMS? (ALARM BEEPING)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,队长！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: On my way. (BREATHING HEAVILY)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰森，快上来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: Johanssen, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(SIGHS)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(STRUGGLING)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,马克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,目前保持在11.5度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: We're at 11.5 and holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,发射准备就绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready to go on your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,准备发射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,队长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,发射前我需要你的口头指令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need you to verbally tell me whether or not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,发射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在中央标准时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS ON TV: At around 4:30 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,凌晨4点30分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Central Standard Time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,卫星检测到火星上有一场风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}our satellites detected a storm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,正在接近战神3号的任务执行地点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}approaching the Ares 3 mission site on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,到6点45分时，风暴情况已十分严峻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At 6:45, the storm had escalated to severe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们别无他法，只能取消任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we had no choice but to abort the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了队长刘易斯的领导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks to the quick action of Commander Lewis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,宇航员贝克，约翰森，马丁内兹和沃格尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}astronauts Beck, Johanssen, Martinez and Vogel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,及时回到了火星飞行器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}were all able to reach the Mars Ascent Vehicle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,并在7点28分完成了紧急撤退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and perform an emergency launch at 7:28 Central Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,然而，在撤退过程中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unfortunately, during the evacuation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,宇航员马克·沃特尼被碎片击中身亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}astronaut Mark Watney was struck by debris and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(REPORTERS GASP) (CAMERAS CLICKING)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,队长刘易斯和其他队员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commander Lewis and the rest of her team...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,成功和赫尔墨斯号对接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}were able to intercept safely with the Hermes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,正在返回地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and are now heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是马克·沃特尼已经殉职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Mark Watney is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德斯局长！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}FEMALE REPORTER: Director Sanders!
