Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果氧合器坏了，我会窒息而死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the oxygenator breaks, I'm gonna suffocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果水回收器坏了，我会渴死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the water reclaimer breaks, I'll die of thirst.
