Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以对我来说，这些食物可以够吃300天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So for just me, that's gonna last 300 sols...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我每天定量摄取，应该能坚持到400天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which I figure I can stretch to 400 if I ration.
