Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个不毛之地上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}three years' worth of food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,给自己种出三年的口粮来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On a planet where nothing grows.
