Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在铱催化剂作用下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I run the hydrazine over an iridium catalyst,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它能分解成氮气和氢气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it'll separate into N2 and H2.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.37,0:25:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,然后将氢气引到一个特定区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then if I just direct the hydrogen into a small area...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.87,0:25:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,点火燃烧即可\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.04,0:25:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,值得庆幸的是，在人类历史上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Luckily, in the history of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.17,0:25:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,用火燃烧氢气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}nothing bad has ever happened
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.01,0:25:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,从没发生什么坏事儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from lighting hydrogen on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.51,0:25:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,航天局那些人不喜欢火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}NASA hates fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.39,0:25:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们总说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because of the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.64,0:26:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“太空里玩火会引火烧身”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"fire makes everybody die in space" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.72,0:26:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，他们给我们用的一切东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, everything they sent us up here with
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.81,0:26:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都是阻燃材料做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is flame-retardant...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.39,0:26:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，我所说的不包括\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the notable exception of...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.69,0:26:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁内兹的私人物品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Martinez's personal items.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.53,0:26:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了，马丁内兹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am sorry, Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.86,0:26:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想让我乱翻你的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if you didn't want me to go through your stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.49,0:26:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不该把我丢在这儿等死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you shouldn't have left me for dead on a desolate planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.87,0:26:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想，鉴于我的这种情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By the way, I'm figuring you're gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.41,0:26:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该不会生气的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}fine with this, given my present situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.83,0:26:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}THE FONZ ON TV: What's everybody doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.91,0:26:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}Taking a holiday from being cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.08,0:26:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,靠你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.50,0:26:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(BLOWING)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.76,0:26:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(SIZZLING)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.10,0:26:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.73,0:26:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(GROANS)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.77,0:26:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(EARS RINGING)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.28,0:27:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，没错，我把自己炸飞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, yeah, I blew myself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.95,0:27:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很有可能是因为…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Best guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.29,0:27:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我在计算的时候忘记了…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I forgot to account for the excess oxygen...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.63,0:27:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,把自己呼出的氧气算进去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I've been exhaling when I did my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.80,0:27:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是蠢到家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.64,0:27:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我等会儿再回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I'm gonna get back to work here...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.89,0:27:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我的耳朵叫个不停\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just as soon as my ears stop ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.27,0:27:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一个有趣的事情是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interesting side note,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.61,0:27:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喷气推进实验室也是这么成立的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this is actually how the Jet Propulsion Lab was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.61,0:27:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,加州理工学院的五个家伙想制造火箭燃料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Five guys at Caltech were trying to make rocket fuel...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.24,0:27:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还差点把自己的宿舍烧了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they nearly burned down their dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.74,0:27:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,学校不但没有开除他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And rather than expel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.24,0:27:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,反倒把他们赶去附近的一个农场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they banished them to a nearby farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.29,0:27:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他们继续完成实验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}told them to keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.66,0:27:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样，我们才有了今天的太空计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now we have a space program.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.58,0:27:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(GASPS)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.08,0:27:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.09,0:28:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(SNORING)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.43,0:28:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,第48个太阳日
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.98,0:28:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,第54个太阳日
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.50,0:29:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊，小家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.22,0:29:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这个国家感到十分荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: The nation was blessed
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.72,0:29:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,能有像马克这样的人才参与太空计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to have Mark serving in our space program.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.84,0:29:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在深感悲痛的同时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}While his loss will be deeply felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.26,0:29:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,航天局的所有工作人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the men and women of NASA will soldier forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.06,0:29:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,依然致力于推进航天事业的发展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}onward and upward in the mission of their agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.43,0:29:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an6}泰迪·桑德斯\N航天局局长
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.52,0:29:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有幸可以接替\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By doing so, they honor the legacy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.86,0:29:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,马克未完成的事业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mark's leaving behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.02,0:29:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,并保证马克的牺牲没有白费\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they ensure his sacrifice will not be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.00,0:29:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(256,192)\an5}约翰逊太空中心\N休斯顿，德克萨斯州
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.31,0:29:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(44,185)\an1}文森特·卡普尔\N火星任务负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.37,0:29:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我很荣幸的说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have the honor of speaking
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.79,0:29:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅是NASA的职员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not only for the men and women of NASA...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.96,0:30:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,并且也是全世界的人们...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but for people all over the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.71,0:30:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你的演讲很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VINCENT: I thought you gave a lovely speech, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.63,0:30:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(TURNS OFF TV)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.80,0:30:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你批准我使用卫星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need you to authorize my satellite time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.63,0:30:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.30,0:30:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,国会资助了我们五次战神任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're funded for five Ares missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.31,0:30:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我可以说服国会再批准一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I can get Congress to authorize a sixth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.81,0:30:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.33,0:30:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,战神3任务只完成了18天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ares 3 evac'd after 18 sols.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.10,0:30:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,火星上还剩一半的物资储备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's half a mission worth of supplies up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.35,0:30:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我此次的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can sell it at a fraction
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.48,0:30:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要使用一小部分资金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the cost of a normal mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.98,0:30:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想知道火星上还剩下些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and all I have to know is what's left of our assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.48,0:30:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是你一个人需要用卫星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not the only one who needs satellite time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.15,0:30:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,战神4任务的补给计划就要开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got the Ares 4 supply missions coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.24,0:30:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的任务重点是夏帕雷利环形山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We should be focusing on the Schiaparelli Crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.57,0:30:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有12个卫星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, we got 12 satellites up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.66,0:30:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我可以使用几个小时…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Surely we can spare a few hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.78,0:30:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的不是这个问题，文斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not about the satellite time, Vince.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.95,0:30:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是一个公开领域的组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're a public domain organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.54,0:30:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所有行动都要公开透明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to be transparent on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.66,0:30:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.79,0:30:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦卫星指向居住舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The second we point the satellites at the Hab...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.62,0:30:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就相当于把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I broadcast pictures
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.75,0:30:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,马克·沃特尼的尸体照片发给世界各地了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of Mark Watney's dead body to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.63,0:30:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是害怕舆论的压力吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're afraid of a PR problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.25,0:30:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然害怕舆论压力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course I'm afraid of a PR problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.01,0:30:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还说其他任务？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Another mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.38,0:30:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果尸体的照片上了华盛顿邮报头条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Congress won't reimburse us for a paper clip...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.89,0:30:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,国会连一个子儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if I put a dead astronaut on the front page
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.68,0:30:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会拨给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of The Washington Post.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.18,0:30:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他会一直在那里的，泰迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not going anywhere, Teddy. I mean, he's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.14,0:30:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他的尸体不会分解腐烂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not gonna decompose, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.14,0:30:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他会永远在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's gonna be up there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.60,0:31:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不出意外的话，气象预测在未来的一年里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meteorology estimates that he'll be covered in sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.56,0:31:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他会被风沙掩埋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from normal weather activity within a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.44,0:31:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等不了一年，还有工作要做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't wait a year. We got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.36,0:31:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,战神5号五年以后才会发射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ares 5 won't even launch for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.07,0:31:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们时间多的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.95,0:31:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.37,0:31:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.53,0:31:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样，设想一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, consider this. (CLEARS THROAT)
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.20,0:31:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，整个世界是站在我们这边的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right now, the world's on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.79,0:31:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很同情沃特尼的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sympathy for the Watney family.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.63,0:31:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,战神6号可以把他的遗体带回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ares 6 could bring his body home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.92,0:31:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，这并不是任务的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, we don't say that's the purpose of the mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.88,0:31:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们可以明确说，这是任务的其中一个计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we make it clear that that would be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.93,0:31:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就这样跟外界说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We frame it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.64,0:31:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们就能得到国会的支持，当然前提是不能等一年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More support from Congress. But not if we wait a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.76,0:31:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一年以后，谁他妈还在乎这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We wait a year, nobody gives a shit.
