Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.67,0:32:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,文森特·卡普尔？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vincent Kapoor?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.64,0:32:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,6-2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}6-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.23,0:32:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,7-6-2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}7-6-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.40,0:32:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阿西达利亚平原\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acidalia Planitia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.95,0:32:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.14,0:32:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,安保吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hi. Security?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.55,0:32:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是卫星通讯员明迪·帕克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Mindy Park in SatCon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.22,0:33:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急情况，我需要联系文森特·卡普尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need the emergency contact for Vincent Kapoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.52,0:33:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.44,0:33:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，是紧急情况！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, it's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.82,0:33:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(256,235)\an5}凌晨2点30分
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.36,0:33:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,确定吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: How sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.90,0:33:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,百分之百确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.57,0:33:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got to be shitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.08,0:33:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(44,200)\an1}安妮·蒙特罗斯\N航天局媒体公关主管
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.45,0:33:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,证明给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: Prove it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.66,0:33:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,首先\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For a start...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.33,0:33:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳能电池板变干净了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the solar panels have been cleaned.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.33,0:33:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也有可能是风吹干净的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They could have been cleaned by wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.37,0:33:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,退回去，看2号探测车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Back it up. Look at Rover 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.92,0:33:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,根据日志记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}According to the logs,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.00,0:33:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,刘易斯队长在第17个太阳日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commander Lewis took it out on Sol 17...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.17,0:33:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,开到居住舱充电\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}plugged it into the Hab to recharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.76,0:33:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,车子位置变化了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's been moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.26,0:33:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她有可能忘记记录位置变化了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She could have forgotten to log the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.26,0:33:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不太可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.64,0:33:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不直接问刘易斯呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ANNIE: Why don't we just ask Lewis?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.93,0:33:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们联系通讯员，直接问清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's get on CAPCOM and ask her directly right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.81,0:33:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.85,0:33:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沃特尼还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If Watney is really alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.06,0:33:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们决不能让他的队友们知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we don't want the Ares 3 crew to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.35,0:33:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能把他们蒙在鼓里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How can you not tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.85,0:33:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还要10个月才能返回地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have another 10 months on their trip home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.07,0:33:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太空航行危险重重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space travel is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.32,0:33:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必须保持警惕，不能受任何事情干扰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They need to be alert and undistracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.03,0:33:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他们认为马克已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But they already think he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.40,0:33:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们知道马克被他们抛弃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they'd be devastated to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.70,0:33:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们肯定更加痛不欲生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they left him there alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.53,0:33:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没有想清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ANNIE: I'm sorry, but you have not thought this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.99,0:34:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要怎么对外界说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are we gonna say? "Dear America...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.16,0:34:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“亲爱的民众，还记得那个已经死去”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"remember that astronaut we killed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.91,0:34:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“并风光下葬的宇航员吗？”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"and had a really nice funeral for?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.50,0:34:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“没想到他还活着，被我们抛弃在火星上了，真是不好意思”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Turns out he's alive and we left him on Mars. Our bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.38,0:34:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,“诚挚问候你们，航天局敬上”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Sincerely, NASA."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.00,0:34:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们要经受多少舆论攻击吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you realize the shitstorm that is about to hit us?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.59,0:34:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要怎么向公众交代？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How are we going to handle the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.34,0:34:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,按理说，24小时内我们必须得发布这些照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Legally, we have 24 hours to release these pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.14,0:34:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,发布照片时附上说明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We release a statement with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.47,0:34:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能让民众瞎猜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't want people working it out on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.06,0:34:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是，局长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.60,0:34:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我没算错的话，在我们能帮到他前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if my math is right, he's going to starve to death
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.56,0:34:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他早就饿死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}long before we can help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.98,0:34:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢想象他在火星得多难熬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you imagine what he's going through up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.48,0:34:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,距离地球5千万公里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's 50 million miles away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.40,0:34:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,独自一人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He thinks he's totally alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.86,0:34:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他认为我们抛弃了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He thinks we gave up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.20,0:34:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这对他的心理该是多大的摧残？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does that do to a man, psychologically?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.29,0:34:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他此时此刻在想什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What the hell is he thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.16,0:34:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(DISCO MUSIC PLAYING)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.58,0:34:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我再继续听下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm definitely gonna die up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.29,0:34:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对会被这烂掉渣的迪斯科音乐折磨死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if I have to listen to any more god-awful disco music.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.80,0:34:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊，刘易斯队长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My God, Commander Lewis,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.34,0:35:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你带来的音乐简直是老掉牙了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}couldn't you have packed anything from this century?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.43,0:35:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着旋律起舞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WOMAN: Turn the beat around
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.14,0:35:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我才不要跟着旋律起舞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, lam not gonna "turn the beat around."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.31,0:35:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I refuse to. (MUSIC STOPS)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.56,0:35:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德斯局长？桑德斯局长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}(REPORTERS CLAMORING) Mr. Sanders? Mr. Sanders?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.31,0:35:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为了联系马克·沃特尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What attempts have been made
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.44,0:35:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们做了哪些努力？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to make contact with Mark Watney?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.40,0:35:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在继续努力中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.44,0:35:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他有足够的补给存活下去吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does he have enough supplies to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.15,0:35:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽快调查的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be looking into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.90,0:35:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这对航天局有什么影响？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does this say about the agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.36,0:35:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你会辞职吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you gonna resign?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.62,0:35:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.74,0:35:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德斯局长！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Director Sanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.24,0:35:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,第70个太阳日
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.37,0:35:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候做长远打算了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: It's time to start thinking long term.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.33,0:35:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,下次航天局的任务是战神4号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The next NASA mission is Ares 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.63,0:35:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,降落地点是夏帕雷利环形山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and it's supposed to land at Schiaparelli Crater...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.55,0:35:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在3200公里之外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}3200 kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.01,0:35:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,3200公里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}3,200 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.30,0:35:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,四年之后，战神4号的队员抵达时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In four years, when the next Ares crew arrives,
