Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.21,0:41:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.38,0:41:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再让文森特接受采访，明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No more Vincent on TV. Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.96,0:41:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,76公里，这是真的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}76 kilometers. Am I reading that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.38,0:41:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你在问我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MINDY: Are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.97,0:41:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: l am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.01,0:41:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.26,0:41:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,马克从居住舱出发，直行两小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mark drove two hours straight away from the Hab...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.43,0:41:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,出舱活动后又开了两个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}did a short EVA and then drove for another two.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.48,0:41:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他出舱活动应该是为了换电池\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We think the EVA was to change batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.35,0:41:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有带上氧合器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He didn't load up the oxygenator
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.77,0:41:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,或者水回收器吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or the water reclaimer?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.27,0:41:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,每隔41小时，我们就会有17分钟的盲区时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every 41 hours, there's a 17 minute gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.11,0:41:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,由于卫星轨道的工作方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's just the way the orbits work...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.19,0:41:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，我们可能会错过一些事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so it's possible that we missed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.24,0:41:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,把盲区时间降到4分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want that gap down to four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.07,0:41:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在把调整轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm giving you total authority
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.87,0:41:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,和卫星轨迹的授权给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}over satellite trajectories and orbital adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.25,0:41:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别让我失望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.62,0:41:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.42,0:41:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们假设帕克小姐没有遗漏任何事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's assume Miss Park didn't miss anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.67,0:41:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说，马克目前还没到达战神4号任务地点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So Mark's not going to Ares 4. Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.25,0:41:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，他也知道这是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But he's smart enough to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.67,0:41:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他活下去的唯一希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's his only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.76,0:41:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯，补给最早什么时候可以送到火星？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bruce, what's the earliest we can get a pre-supply there?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.68,0:42:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于目前地球和火星的相对位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With the positions of Earth and Mars,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.22,0:42:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(44,200)\an1}布鲁斯·吴\N喷气推进实验室主任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}\N
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.22,0:42:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一共需要9个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it'll take nine months.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.02,0:42:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,设备的建造就要花费6个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll take six months to build it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.35,0:42:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你3个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.94,0:42:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,3个月？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.02,0:42:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你会说不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: You're going to say it's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.31,0:42:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就会做个发言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then I'm gonna make a speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.90,0:42:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,夸奖你们实验室丰功伟绩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about the blinding capabilities
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.11,0:42:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没有做不到的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the JPL team...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.40,0:42:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你想想之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then you're going to do the math
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.53,0:42:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就会对我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in your head and say something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.74,0:42:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,“加班加点工作是个噩梦”之类的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"The overtime alone will be a nightmare."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.82,0:42:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,加班加点工作本来就是个噩梦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The overtime alone will be a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.95,0:42:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,快开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: Get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.12,0:42:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我来筹集资金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll find you the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.70,0:42:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得告诉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to tell the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.43,0:42:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(44,185)\an1}米奇·亨德森\N赫尔墨斯号飞行指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.66,0:42:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇，这个我们讨论过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VINCENT: Mitch, we've discussed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.75,0:42:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不，是你自己擅自决定的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you discussed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.42,0:42:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是那个小组的负责人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm the one who decides what's best for the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.96,0:42:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有权知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They deserve to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.80,0:42:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等救援计划落实了，我们自然会告诉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Once there's a real rescue plan, we'll tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.80,0:42:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在说没有任何意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Otherwise, it's moot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.59,0:42:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯有3个月时间来做准备工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bruce has three months to get the payload done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.18,0:42:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是目前最重要的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's all that matters right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.14,0:42:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽力的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.85,0:42:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,马克的命运就在你们手上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mark dies if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.60,0:42:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,第79个太阳日
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.94,0:42:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,距离我种下土豆已经过去48个太阳日了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: It's been 48 sols since I planted the potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.61,0:42:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候收获果实，重新播种了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So now it's time to reap and re-sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.82,0:42:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,它们比预期长得还好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They grew even better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.53,0:43:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，我有400棵土豆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I now have 400 healthy potato plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.62,0:43:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我把土豆挖出来，并保持植株成活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I dug them up, being careful to leave their plants alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.95,0:43:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小颗的重新种下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The smaller ones I'll reseed,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.54,0:43:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大颗的作为食品供应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the larger ones are my food supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.87,0:43:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,纯天然，有机的火星土豆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All natural, organic, Martian-grown potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.84,0:43:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事情不太常见，对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't hear that every day, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.80,0:43:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，如果联系不上航天局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And by the way, none of this matters at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.63,0:43:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,种再多的土豆也无济于事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if I can't figure out a way to make contact with NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.32,0:43:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我有办法了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what I'm gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.44,0:44:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他又行动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh! He's moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.73,0:44:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底是要去哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where the hell is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.27,0:44:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经连续13天没改变方向了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He hasn't changed course for 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.61,0:44:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,行驶方向也不是朝着战神4号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's nowhere near the Ares 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.11,0:44:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,或许他走了一些弯路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unless he's not taking a direct route.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.03,0:44:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,比如想避开一些障碍什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He might be trying to avoid some obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.24,0:44:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有什么障碍？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What obstacle?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.95,0:44:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是阿西达利亚平原\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's Acidalia Planitia.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.29,0:44:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那里什么都没有，除了…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's nothing out there except the...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.71,0:44:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,除了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.30,0:44:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要找一张地图\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.60,0:44:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.31,0:44:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计，你在干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, come on. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.73,0:44:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没事，没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's all right. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.89,0:44:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我能借下这个吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I borrow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.27,0:44:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好，他的居住舱在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, so where is the Hab location?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.44,0:44:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,北纬31.2°，西经28.5°\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}31.2 degrees north, 28.5 degrees west.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.27,0:44:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay. Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.44,0:45:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特尼现在在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's Watney? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.49,0:45:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.65,0:45:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VINCENT: Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.95,0:45:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他要去哪儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay. I know where he's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.12,0:45:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去赶飞机了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need to get on an airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.96,0:45:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(PANTING)
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.69,0:45:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,200)\an3}喷气推进实验室\N帕萨迪纳，加利福尼亚州
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.37,0:45:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,文森特，你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vincent, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.66,0:45:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.95,0:45:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行还顺利吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good flight? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.49,0:45:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.33,0:45:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,它就放在那个角落的仓库里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's in storage just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.16,0:46:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,文森特，很高兴再次见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, Vincent, nice to see you again.
