Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.55,1:02:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就像以前在赫尔墨斯号上一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Big data dumps like when I was on the Hermes.
