Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.30,1:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有照片给你就不错了，安妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just be grateful we got you something, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.14,1:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这个照片不能用，文森特，你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't use this, Vincent, and you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.26,1:03:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要一张他的正脸照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need a picture of his face.
