Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.32,1:03:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,发送物资补给到火星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}during the Hohmann Transfer Window.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.40,1:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯，你们的工作在进度之内吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bruce, your team's still on schedule?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.82,1:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然日程很紧，但是我们可以做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll be tight, but we'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.91,1:03:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,9个月的行程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nine-month travel time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.49,1:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的探测器在第868个太阳日才能到火星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That puts the probe to Mars on Sol 868.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.16,1:03:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,植物学家那边的数据分析拿到了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did we get the botany team's analysis?
