Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.42,1:04:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很不情愿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grudgingly?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.50,1:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，因为只要他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. Mark has a tendency to tell them
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.59,1:04:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,质疑马克的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to have sex with themselves...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.76,1:04:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,马克就会对他们爆粗口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}whenever they question one of his decisions.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.80,1:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,让他注意点，文森特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: Get him in line, Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.97,1:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事不能有任何偏差\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't afford any miscommunication.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.10,1:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌事情没有余地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hate this margin.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.39,1:04:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,912天的食物，我们的补给第868天才能到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}912 Sols worth of food. We get there on 868.
