Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.32,1:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,居住舱的食物够他撑409个太阳日，对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rations get him to what? Sol 409?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.53,1:09:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，加上土豆的话，可以撑到第609天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mmm-hmm. So with potatoes, 609.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.36,1:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以到第868个太阳日，他早就死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So by Sol 868, he'll be long dead.
