Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.87,1:23:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一个伟大…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"for something big...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.91,1:23:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,壮丽…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"and beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.92,1:23:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,高于个人的事业而牺牲的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"and greater than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.80,1:23:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我能接受这样的结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Tell them I said I can live with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.47,1:23:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,最后，告诉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"And tell them...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.30,1:23:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢他们带我来到这个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"thank you for being my mom and dad."
