Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.56,1:23:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们使用蛋白块\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VINCENT: We substituted protein cubes
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.65,1:23:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,作为每天的食粮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for the standard rations.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.90,1:23:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,发射时的推力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The thrust of the launch combined
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.73,1:23:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,加上同时的横向振动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the simultaneous lateral vibration...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.61,1:24:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,导致蛋白块液化，从而使负载失衡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}liquefied the cubes and created an unbalanced load.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.49,1:24:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,文森特，这种情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vincent, why wasn't this addressed
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.95,1:24:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么检查环节时没有发现？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the inspections phase?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.66,1:24:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为为了能赶上发射期限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In order to make our launch window,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.29,1:24:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被迫加速了整个流程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we were forced to accelerate our schedule.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.04,1:24:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(BOTH SPEAKING MAN DARIN)
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.16,1:24:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的宇航员将会饿死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Their astronaut is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.92,1:24:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(44,175)\an1}郭明\N中国航天局首席科学家
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.13,1:24:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，还有其他的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course there are other ways...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.35,1:24:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(76,165)\an1}朱涛\N中国航天局副首席科学家
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.26,1:24:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳神的助推器，我们的工程师检查过数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the Taiyang Shen booster. Our engineers have run the numbers,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.26,1:24:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,它的容量可以到达火星的轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and it has enough fuel for a Mars injection orbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.18,1:24:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,NASA为什么没有找我们？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why hasn't NASA approached us?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.93,1:24:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.52,1:24:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的数据是绝密的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our booster technology is classified.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.60,1:24:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说，假如我们什么都不做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So if we do nothing...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.15,1:24:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,世界将永远不会知道，其实，我们是可以帮的上忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world would never know we could have helped.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.28,1:24:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，仅仅是为了论证，如果我们决定帮助他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then, for the sake of argument, let's say we decide to help them...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.79,1:24:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把助推器给了他们，也就是取消了太阳神计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'd be giving up a booster and effectively cancelling Taiyang Shen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.79,1:24:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就从航天的角度来解决问题，寻求合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to keep this among scientists, a co-operation between space agencies.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.72,1:25:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.22,1:25:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.14,1:25:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.98,1:25:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.23,1:25:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(SIGHS)
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.40,1:25:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}BRUCE: All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.52,1:25:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢我的中国叔叔汤米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks to my uncle Tommy in China,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.23,1:25:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we get another chance at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.23,1:25:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,上次，我们花62天完成了探测器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, we finished the Iris probe in 62 days.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.49,1:25:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这次，我们要在28天内完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are now gonna attempt to finish it in 28.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.55,1:25:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(256,279)}昴宿星团，航天局超级计算机
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.08,1:25:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(CHIMES)
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.19,1:25:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,计算正确
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.56,1:25:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以抛弃着陆系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can jettison any kind of landing system.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.93,1:25:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只发送食物补给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're only sending rations.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.52,1:25:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在火星实现摔机着陆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can crash-land on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.56,1:25:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该把电话挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You should hang up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.23,1:26:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是哪位？- 我是里奇·珀内尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, who are you? My name is Rich Purnell.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.36,1:26:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是天体动力学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I work in Astrodynamics,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.44,1:26:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在应该把电话挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you should hang up the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.86,1:26:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.70,1:26:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我回头打给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna call you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.41,1:26:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么能救马克·沃特尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know how to save Mark Watney.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.12,1:26:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的探测器计划不可行，会出现很多差错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your probe plan won't work. Too many things can go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.79,1:26:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我有更好的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got a better way.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.96,1:26:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你是天体动力学家？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Astrodynamics?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.21,1:26:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.96,1:26:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,“艾隆德计划”是个什么东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What the hell is "Project Elrond"?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.92,1:26:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我得给计划起个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VINCENT: I had to make something up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.09,1:26:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是“艾隆德”是什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But "Elrond"?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.93,1:26:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是一个秘密会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because it's a secret meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.14,1:26:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.26,1:26:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么“艾隆德”代表“秘密会议”？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why does "Elrond" mean "secret meeting"?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.85,1:26:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,艾隆德会议，出自指环王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Council of Elrond. It's from Lord of the Rings.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.60,1:26:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,指环王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lord of the Rings.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.73,1:26:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个会议上他们决定毁掉那个魔戒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the meeting where they decide to destroy the One Ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.02,1:26:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要叫“艾隆德计划”的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: If we're gonna call something "Project Elrond"...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.86,1:26:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我的代号叫“格洛芬德尔”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would like my code name to be "Glorfindel."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.19,1:26:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌你们每一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, I hate every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.28,1:26:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什么，连泰迪都不知道这个计划？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What, Teddy doesn't even know about this yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.90,1:26:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，你是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.20,1:26:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他是里奇·珀内尔，天体动力学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VINCENT: This is Rich Purnell, Astrodynamics.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.03,1:26:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,把你刚才说的告诉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell them what you just told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.79,1:26:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以让赫尔墨斯号在第561个太阳日回到火星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can get the Hermes back to Mars by Sol 561.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.54,1:26:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: HOW?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.67,1:27:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你能站到那儿吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could you stand right there for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.05,1:27:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.22,1:27:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那儿，很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right there. Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.47,1:27:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你能站到那里吗，那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And could you stand right there? Right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.35,1:27:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,假设这个订书机是赫尔墨斯号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, let's pretend that this stapler is the Hermes...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.31,1:27:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you are...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.73,1:27:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，你叫什么来着？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, what's your name again?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.11,1:27:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,泰迪，现任航天局局长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Teddy. I'm the Director of NASA.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.82,1:27:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,酷，泰迪，你是地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cool. Teddy, you're Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.12,1:27:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，赫尔墨斯号正驶向地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And right now, the Hermes is headed towards you...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.49,1:27:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时，开始减速，准备和地球对接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}starting its month-long deceleration to intercept.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.16,1:27:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，我的建议是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But instead, what I'm proposing is...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.75,1:27:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(WHOOSHING)
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.67,1:27:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就应该开始加速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we start accelerating immediately
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.01,1:27:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,从而达到更高的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to preserve velocity and gain even more.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.84,1:27:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不需要和地球对接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't intercept with Earth at all...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.13,1:27:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是可以足够靠近地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we come close enough
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.55,1:27:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来获得引力助推，并改变航向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to get a gravity assist and adjust course.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.85,1:27:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}While we're doing that...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.93,1:27:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们用探测器实现食物补给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we resupply with the probe...
