Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.68,1:32:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样，我尽力把所有事情都记录下来，分类好.\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anyway, I'm trying to keep everything documented, organized.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.27,1:32:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这不是我的强项\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know it's not my strong suit...
