Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.28,1:33:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,做一个淋浴间.\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}using NASA tubing and an old RTG.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.12,1:33:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如何用6000种方式烤土豆.\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How to cook a potato about 6,000 different ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.04,1:33:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,马克·沃特尼的教学大纲.\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Mark Watney syllabus.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.18,1:33:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 约翰森，你在吗？- 我在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VOGEL: Johanssen? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.85,1:33:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道现在是私人时间，但是我能打扰你一下吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know it's your private time. Can I bother you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.52,1:33:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可以，说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}JOHANSSEN: Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.61,1:33:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VOGEL: Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.69,1:33:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,健身房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The gym.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.00,1:33:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(BEEPS)
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.59,1:33:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(PANTING)
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.51,1:34:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.88,1:34:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我老婆给我的一封邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just got an email from my wife
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.01,1:34:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,主题栏写的是“我们的孩子”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the subject line says, "Our children."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.26,1:34:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我的电脑打不开附件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My computer won't open the attachment.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.68,1:34:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.06,1:34:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我来看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.10,1:34:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.69,1:34:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.03,1:34:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是图片文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This isn't a JPEG.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.40,1:34:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个ASCII码文本文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a plain ASCII text file.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.70,1:34:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道这文件什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't really know what we're looking at.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.70,1:34:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看懂吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does that make any sense to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.37,1:34:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,里奇·珀内尔机动策略\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Rich Purnell Maneuver."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.71,1:34:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是新的赫尔墨斯号航线策略\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a course maneuver for the Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.55,1:34:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这个任务要求在第211个太阳日终止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the mission concludes with Earth intercept,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.89,1:34:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,与地球对接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}211 days later.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.27,1:34:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这个计划能行吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}MARTINEZ: Would it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.89,1:34:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们测试了数据，没有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Mmm-hmm. We ran the numbers. They check out.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.06,1:34:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个计划太聪明了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}BECK: It's a brilliant course.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.60,1:35:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么我们还要秘密行动？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So why all the cloak and dagger?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.61,1:35:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为航天局不允许我们这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because it goes directly against NASA's decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.57,1:35:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，但是如果我们这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. If we do the maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.61,1:35:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们别无他法，只能给我们发送补给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they'd have to send the supply ship or we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.91,1:35:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们有机会改变他们的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have the opportunity to force their hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.28,1:35:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢，我们要做吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, are we gonna do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.95,1:35:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我来决定，我们早就在去火星的路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it was up to me, we'd already be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.08,1:35:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但这就是你能决定的事啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it is, though, isn't it? Up to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.75,1:35:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}(CHUCKLES) Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.00,1:35:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个计划被航天局否决了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is something NASA expressly rejected.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.80,1:35:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果行动，就是违抗命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're talking about mutiny here,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.63,1:35:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不能一个人决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which is not a word that I take lightly.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.26,1:35:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要么大家都同意，要么放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So we do this together or not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.97,1:35:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在你答应之前，想想这次行动的后果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And before you answer, consider the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.10,1:35:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果补给对接失败，我们会没命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we mess up the supply rendezvous, we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.31,1:35:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果借助地球引力助推失败，我们也会没命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we mess up the Earth gravity assist, we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.27,1:35:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就算一切都没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we do everything perfectly...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.48,1:35:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要延长任务533天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we add 533 days to our mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.78,1:35:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,533天以后才能再次和家人团聚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}533 more days before we see our families again.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.82,1:35:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,533天计划外的太空行程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}533 days of unplanned space travel...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.50,1:35:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都有可能出差错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where anything could go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.21,1:36:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果任务没成功，我们还是会没命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it's mission critical, we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.46,1:36:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,算上我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sign me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.67,1:36:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别激动，牛仔.\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, cowboy, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.30,1:36:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我都是军人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and I, we're military.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.13,1:36:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回去就有可能上军事法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Chances are, we go home, they'll court martial us.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.88,1:36:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是有这个可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, there's that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.97,1:36:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,至于其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: And for the rest of you guys...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.18,1:36:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信，他们不可能再让你们参与太空任务了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I guarantee they will never send you back up here again.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.18,1:36:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了，如果我们答应的话，计划怎么执行？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. So, if we go for it, how would it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.81,1:36:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我来制定航线，并负责执行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I plot the course and execute it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.52,1:36:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,远程操控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}JOHANSSEN: Remote override.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.98,1:36:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们完全可以从任务指挥中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They could take over the Hermes
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.23,1:36:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,来远程控制赫尔墨斯号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from Mission Control.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.69,1:36:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你能解除吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Can you disable it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.82,1:36:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,赫尔墨斯号有4台备用计算机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hermes has four redundant flight computers...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.07,1:36:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,每台计算机又连接3个备用通讯系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}each connected to three redundant comm systems.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.53,1:36:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果关掉通讯系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't shut down the comms
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.87,1:36:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就失去了遥测和导航功能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because we'd lose telemetry and guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.53,1:36:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果关掉计算机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we can't shut down the computers
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.16,1:36:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,整个飞船都无法运行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because we need to run the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.00,1:36:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我得解除每个系统的远程操控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd have to disable remote override on each system.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.50,1:36:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我得想办法跳过系统代码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's part of the OS, I'd have to jump over the code.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.58,1:36:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，说人话，你能做到吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, but, like, in English, what would that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.26,1:36:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.51,1:36:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.22,1:36:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,并且，这必须是集体同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it has to be unanimous.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.51,1:37:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这么做的话，在太空就要待上900多天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we do this, it'll be over 900 days of space.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.52,1:37:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一辈子的太空任务加起来也没这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's more than enough space for one life...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.77,1:37:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，我同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.53,1:37:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我也同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I vote yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.20,1:37:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去接他回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's go get him.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.62,1:37:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰森呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Johanssen?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.29,1:37:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.70,1:37:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah! (ALL CHEERING)
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.04,1:37:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(APPLAUSE)
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.00,1:37:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特尼，我们来救你
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.00,1:37:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,接收到新的文本消息
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.00,1:37:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特尼，我们来救你
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.90,1:37:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们打算怎么做呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But how are you gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.15,1:37:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,赫尔墨斯号有计划外的状态更新\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Got an unscheduled status update from Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.94,1:37:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,收到，读出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}BRENDAN: Roger. Read it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.11,1:37:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,“休斯顿，请注意”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Message reads, "Houston, please be advised.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.91,1:37:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,“里奇·珀内尔是个绝妙的天才”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Rich Purnell is a steely-eyed missile man."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.82,1:37:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.91,1:37:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥官，导航台\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}GUIDANCE TECHNICIAN: Flight, Guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.49,1:38:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,检测到赫尔墨斯号偏离航线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hermes is off-course.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.45,1:38:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯员，通知他们已偏离航线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}CAPCOM, advise Hermes they're drifting.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.83,1:38:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,导航台，准备纠正航线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guidance, get a correction ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.58,1:38:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,无法纠正，指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}GUIDANCE TECHNICIAN: Negative, Flight,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.59,1:38:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是航线偏离，而是他们改变了航线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's not drift. They've adjusted course.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.42,1:38:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What the hell?
