Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.43,1:38:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是里奇·珀内尔？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}(WHISPERS) Hey. Who's Rich Purnell?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.64,1:38:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.31,1:38:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能告诉我这个里奇·珀内尔到底是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will somebody find out who the hell Rich Purnell is?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.98,1:38:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮今早会通知媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}SANDERS: Annie will go before the media this morning...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.11,1:38:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,航天局作出决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and inform them of NASA's decision
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.77,1:38:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让赫尔墨斯号重返火星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to reroute the Hermes to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.78,1:38:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,挺明智的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sounds like a smart move.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.45,1:38:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到他们已经这么做的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Considering the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.28,1:38:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是谁通知了他们都没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whoever gave them the maneuver only passed along information.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.04,1:38:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这个决定是他们自己做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Crew made the decision on their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.62,1:38:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可能因为你而丧命，米奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may have killed them, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.63,1:38:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们坐的是同一条船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're fighting the same war.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.50,1:38:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,每次出现问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every time something goes wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.01,1:38:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,外界就不管初衷，把我们一棒子打死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the world forgets why we fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.80,1:38:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想保住我们的航天事业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm trying to keep us airborne.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.55,1:38:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这比一个人的生命重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's bigger than one person.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.51,1:39:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.14,1:39:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.48,1:39:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,等这件事结束，我希望能看到你的辞职信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When this is over, I'll expect your resignation.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.48,1:39:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.98,1:39:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们都带回来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bring our astronauts home.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.04,1:39:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,第219个太阳日
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.53,1:39:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,每个战神任务都会提前三年准备物资\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every Ares mission requires three years of pre-supplies.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.41,1:39:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以航天局早就决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So NASA decided a long time ago it's a lot easier...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.16,1:39:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,预先送一些设备到火星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to send some of the stuff beforehand
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.50,1:39:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样比我们自己带过来容易得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}rather than bring it with us.
