Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.92,1:39:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,夏帕雷利环形山那里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at the Schiaparelli Crater, just waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.88,1:39:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以新计划就是，我乘飞行器到达火星轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So the plan is for me to use that to go into orbit...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.88,1:39:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,此时赫尔墨斯号正好经过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just as the Hermes is passing...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.01,1:39:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我猜，他们会接住我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I guess they catch me?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.22,1:39:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太空对接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In space.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.06,1:39:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我有200天的时间来计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, I've got 200 sols to figure out...
