Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.36,1:39:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,比如氧合器，水回收器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the oxygenator, the water reclaimer,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.11,1:39:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大气调节器等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the atmospheric regulator...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.20,1:40:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}bring that all with me.
