Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.19,1:45:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想火星的法律问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: I've been thinking about laws on Mars.
