Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.08,1:45:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,而航天局是一个美国的非军事组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, NASA is an American non-military organization.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.54,1:45:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,居住舱属于他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It owns the Hab.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.71,1:45:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只要我出了居住舱，我就在公海领域上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But the second I walk outside, I'm in international waters.
