Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.28,2:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(ALL CHEERING)
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.24,2:09:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在情况如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: What's your status?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.04,2:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的胸很痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: My chest hurts.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.08,2:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,肋骨断了几根\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I broke my ribs.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.29,2:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:21.54,2:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在想办法救你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: We're working on getting to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:22.71,2:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,发射过程出现了一些问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was a complication during launch.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.38,2:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.30,2:09:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,问题严重吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:27.92,2:09:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们修正了对接距离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: We've corrected the intercept range,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:29.55,2:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是对接速度有很大问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we've got a problem with intercept velocity.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:31.68,2:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,速度是多少？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: How big a problem?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.14,2:09:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,42米每秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}42 meters a second.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.01,2:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那可真是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.31,2:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,操蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.69,2:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，我有个主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commander, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.65,2:09:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,说来听听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Go ahead, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:47.23,2:09:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我用个尖锐物品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if I can find something sharp in here...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.57,2:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的手套上戳个洞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and poke a hole in the glove of my EVA suit...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:53.57,2:09:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我就可以用泄露的气体当助推器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could use the escaping air as a thruster...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.20,2:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,朝你们飞过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and fly towards you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:57.74,2:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这个就在我手上，所以比较容易控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would be easy to control because it would be on my arm.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.08,2:10:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得你这么做能控制任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: I can't see you having any control if you did that.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.08,2:10:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做只能目测进行对接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'd be eyeballing the intercept
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.96,2:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而且推力矢量也无法控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}using a thrust vector you can barely control.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.46,2:10:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，你说得很对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, those are all very good points.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.42,2:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是想想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But consider this.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:16.22,2:10:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我却可以像钢铁侠一样到处飞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd get to fly around like Iron Man.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.06,2:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(JOHANSSEN LAUGHS)
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.18,2:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,队长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: Commander...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:21.93,2:10:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让我当钢铁侠吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}let's go Iron Man.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:26.69,2:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,信号意外丢失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}NASA TECHNICIAN 1: This is unexpected LOS.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.19,2:10:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯信号丢失，待命中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}NASA TECHNICIAN 2: Communication lost. Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.11,2:10:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这主意也许不坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe it's not the worst idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.90,2:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不，这主意坏透了，糟透了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, it is the worst idea. It's the worst idea ever.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:35.91,2:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他说的那些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not what he said.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.20,2:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而是用气体当推力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Using atmosphere as thrust.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.54,2:10:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们可以向前产生一个推力呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happens if we blow the VAL?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.75,2:10:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要打开气密舱吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait, you want to open the vehicular airlock?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:45.79,2:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以产生反冲力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll give us a good kick.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.04,2:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也会把整个飞船的东西都吹走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But also blow the nose off the ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.96,2:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而且空气耗尽，我们也就完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And all the air would leave and we need air to not die.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.92,2:10:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以封锁舱桥和堆舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We would seal the bridge and the reactor room.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.34,2:10:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,其他地方会变成真空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everywhere else would go vacuo.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.22,2:10:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沃格尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vogel.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.30,2:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,请讲，队长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VOGEL: Go ahead, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.01,2:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你回来造个…炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need you to come inside and make a... bomb.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.39,2:11:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,队长，你说什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Again, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.43,2:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个化学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: You're a chemist.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.52,2:11:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你能用现有的东西造个炸弹吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you make a bomb with what you have on board?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.02,2:11:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Probably.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:10.40,2:11:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不得不提醒大家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I feel obliged to mention
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.78,2:11:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在飞船上引爆一个炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that setting off an explosive device...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.74,2:11:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这实在是太不明智的行为了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in a spacecraft is a terrible, terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.82,2:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，你们造炸弹不叫上我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hang on. You guys making a bomb without me?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.87,2:11:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白，你能做到吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Copy that. Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.29,2:11:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ja.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.21,2:11:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，请注意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Houston, be advised.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:29.96,2:11:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备有计划地制造一个飞船缺口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are going to deliberately breach the VAL
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.50,2:11:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来产生反向推力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to produce a reverse thrust.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.26,2:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,贝克，去1号气密舱和约翰森碰头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beck, leave your suit on. Meet Johanssen in Airlock 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:36.84,2:11:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会把外舱门打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll open the outer door.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.05,2:11:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要把炸弹放置在内舱门上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need you to place the charge on the inner door.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.18,2:11:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,然后顺舱体回到2号气密舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Climb back to Airlock 2 along the hull.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:42.47,2:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,收到，行动中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}BECK: Copy. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.57,2:11:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我进来了，队长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.19,2:11:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}LEWIS: Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.41,2:12:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沃格尔，你在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vogel, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.16,2:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我在厨房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}VOGEL: I'm in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:06.37,2:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.38,2:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,队长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: Commander...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.55,2:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让你这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't let you go through with this.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.59,2:12:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备实施我的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am prepared to cut the suit.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:16.47,2:12:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.68,2:12:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧，我这人很自私的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}WATNEY: See, the thing is, I'm selfish.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.30,2:12:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望地球只给我一个人办追悼会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want all the memorials back home to be about me.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.26,2:12:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只纪念我一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just me.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.39,2:12:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该把你留在火星才对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should have left this guy on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.98,2:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey-
Dialogue: 0,2:12:30.90,2:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,白糖？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sugar?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.98,2:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:37.11,2:12:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你能拿着这个吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you hold this?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:39.11,2:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,液态氧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Liquid oxygen...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:40.99,2:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,加上含氨的去污剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and some stain remover that contains ammonia.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.00,2:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这个东西比一般炸药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This thing here is five times stronger
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.38,2:12:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,的威力强5倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than a stick of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:52.88,2:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么才能启动它呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do we activate it?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:54.30,2:12:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,把它连接到照明控制器上就行了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you connect this to one of our lighting panels?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:00.59,2:13:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.43,2:13:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,打开1号气密舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}BECK: Open Airlock 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.77,2:13:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在去和贝克碰头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}JOHANSSEN: I'm on the way to Beck.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:21.24,2:13:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,希望这是个好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's just hope this is a good idea, guys.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:23.20,2:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是个好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:24.33,2:13:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,打开1号气密舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}JOHANSSEN: Open A1.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.87,2:13:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿   - 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hi. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:35.54,2:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿好了？   - 嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You got it? Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:42.72,2:13:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,引爆的时候，你要确保离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make sure you're not in here when this thing goes off.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.14,2:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey-
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.52,2:13:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,出舱的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.52,2:13:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In space.
