Dialogue: 0,2:22:00.01,2:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,请注意听讲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now pay attention,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:01.84,2:22:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我的话可能会救你一命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because this could save your life.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:04.05,2:22:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我，我有亲身体验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Trust me, I know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:05.80,2:22:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00ff00&}(ALL LAUGH)
Dialogue: 0,2:22:06.89,2:22:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,正式开始前我先说两句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me get a few things out of the way, right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:09.14,2:22:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，我是在火星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I did in fact survive on a deserted planet
Dialogue: 0,2:22:12.81,2:22:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,靠屎种地活了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by farming in my own shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:16.06,2:22:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，这个事情比你听起来要糟的多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, it's actually worse than it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:18.61,2:22:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以以后就别再提了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So let's not talk about that ever again.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:21.74,2:22:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我经常被问到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other question I get most frequently is...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.87,2:22:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当我孤身一人在火星上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"When I was up there, stranded by myself...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:27.58,2:22:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有想过会死在那里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"did I think I was going to die?"
Dialogue: 0,2:22:30.45,2:22:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,答案是，当然想过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:33.12,2:22:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你们参加这个项目，也要知道这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that's what you need to know going in
Dialogue: 0,2:22:34.50,2:22:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这很有可能发生在你们身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because it's going to happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:36.59,2:22:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谈论的是太空，太空不会配合你工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is space. It does not cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:40.30,2:22:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候，所有的情况都会对你不利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At some point, everything is going to go south on you.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.22,2:22:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的坏事一起发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything is going to go south
Dialogue: 0,2:22:44.43,2:22:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你就可能会想，就是这样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you're going to say, "This is it.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.22,2:22:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的终点了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"This is how I end."
Dialogue: 0,2:22:49.26,2:22:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,面对这种情况，你要么接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, you can either accept that...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:51.35,2:22:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要么想办法解决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or you can get to work.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:54.39,2:22:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是一切的真谛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.27,2:22:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,解决问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You just begin.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:58.94,2:23:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你想各种办法，解决一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You do the math. You solve one problem...
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.11,2:23:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后接着解决下一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then you solve the next one.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:03.86,2:23:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,循环往复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then the next.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:04.99,2:23:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等你解决了足够多的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if you solve enough problems,
