Dialogue: 0,2:23:34.60,2:23:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这次任务的目标又是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And what do you hope to achieve this time around?
