Dialogue: 0,2:25:53.78,2:25:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx162\fscy162\c&H80ffFF&}起初我很害怕， \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First I was afraid
