Dialogue: 0,2:26:30.07,2:26:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx162\fscy162\c&H80ffFF&}请你转身离开，你已经不受欢迎 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just turn around now 'cause you're not welcome anymore
